* FEP tubes (Bola, S1815-04, inner diameter 0.8 mm, outer diameter 1.6 mm)
* 1 M NaOH (Merck)
* 0.5 M NaOH
* ultrasonicator
* double-distilled H2O
* 70% ethanol
* syringe filter (Millex-HV PVDF 0.45 µm)
* Low-melting-point agarose (Sigma)
* methylcellulose (Sigma)
* E3 (Nüsslein-Volhard and Dahm, 2002)
* glass capillary with Teflon-coated plungers (BRAND)
* needle (100 Sterican, blunt)
* syringe
* Tricaine (Aldrich)

